Alert:
Types: 1.simple alert(accept/dismiss)   2. confirmation alert(ok/cancel)   3.prompt alert(ok/cancel/senddata)

Alert alert = driver.switchTo().alert();
alert.accept();
alert.getText();
or 
driver.switchTo().alert().accept();
driver.switchTo().alert().dismiss();
driver.switchTo().alert().sendKeys("data");
driver.switchTo().alert().getText();


Popup:
Types: 
1.hidden division popup  2.child popup  
3.file upload/download  popup  4.js alert popup  
5.authentication popup 6.permission popup


Both can be handlede according they suite:
1. handle with Alert interface
2. handle with web element method
3. handle with window/tab way
4. handle with Robot class
